headline: Pat Hynes Named President of Prudential Advisors
summary: NEWARK, N.J., February 26, 2025--Pat Hynes has been named president of Prudential Advisors, where he will lead Prudential Financial, Inc.’s (NYSE: PRU) retail and advice arm. This business comprises more than 2,800 financial advisors and fee-based financial planners who offer clients, including more than 3.5 million American families, a full range of financial advice and solutions.
